        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Advanced Nuclear Fuel Availability Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Energy to develop and deploy high-assay low-enriched uranium for domestic commercial use and to develop a schedule for recovering costs associated with such development.</p>]]></text>
